<h4 class="title text-sm p-5 px-0 xl:px-5 font-normal tracking-widest uppercase xl:-ml-5">More from SOFREP</h4>
<div class="related md:flex xl:-mx-2 flex-wrap">
<div class="news-box md:px-2 md:w-1/3">
<a href="https://sofrep.com/news/old-man-fitness-how-to-burn-belly-fat-fast-is-a-bullsht-marketing-gimmick" class="outline-none">
<span class="flex justify-between md:flex-col items-stretch">
<img data-src="https://i0.wp.com/cms.sofrep.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/belly-fat-1.jpg?fit=1200%2C607&amp;ssl=1&amp;resize=350%2C200" alt="Old Man Fitness: How to burn belly fat fast! (Is a bullsh*t marketing gimmick)" class="object-cover w-4/12 h-32 md:w-full md:h-40 order-last md:order-first lazy" />
<div class="content p-5 pl-0 md:px-0 flex flex-col justify-between">
<h3 class="md:text-lg">Old Man Fitness: How to burn belly fat fast! (Is a bullsh*t marketing gimmick)</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Dec 10</span>
</div>
</div>
